Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:38.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s eating the Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:02:00.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Those bindings were what allowed us\Nto control the Eva’s power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But now the Eva is removing the\Nweb that binds it to our will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01’s been awakened and set free!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:11.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,SEELE won’t stay quiet for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:16.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Eva series isn’t capable of\Ngenerating S2 organs themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:20.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But we never imagined that it would\Nbe able to take one into itself this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This incident is at extreme odds with\Nthe scenario SEELE created.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It will not be easy to correct this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:32.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Gendo Ikari...  It was a mistake to\Nentrust NERV to him, wasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:37.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But he was the only one who could\Nachieve this project’s goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari, what’s going on in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s begun, hasn’t it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,Yes, this is the beginning.
