Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:53.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damage on both Evas is over\Nthe Hayflick limit, beyond\Nany normal restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:56.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It may be a while before we can\Nrestore everything to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the MAGI system can be\Ntransferred to a new location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We may be able to start\Nworking tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:04.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But this place will have\Nto be scrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:07.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s just a matter of time before the\Nbrass decides to abandon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:13.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,For the time being, we’ll have to use\Nthe Secondary Command Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You mean, without the MAGI?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can clean the dust off and be\Nworking again by this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:24.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But the chairs are too cramped down\Nthere, and the sensors don’t operate\Nsmoothly.  It’s difficult to work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But at least the layout is the same\Nas our original Command Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It just feels like we don’t belong there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,At least we have an alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We have no choice when it\Ncomes to using Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It may be restrained by the cage,\Nbut are you sure it’s safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:48.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No heat emissions, free electrons,\Nelectromagnetic fields or chemical\Nreactions are being detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The S2 unit is completely inactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:54.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, on three\Nseparate occasions Unit 01 has\Nmoved without power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:02.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You can’t judge this situation just by\Nthe things you can see and measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, we can’t take any chances,\Nthat’s for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s as unpredictable as\Nyou are, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:16.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, our concerns are\Nnot limited to Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.  Serious damage was\Nsustained by Units 00 and 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Headquarters was partially destroyed,\Nexposing Central Dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The destruction was enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:28.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can’t even estimate how much\Nmoney and time have been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This all is because we didn’t put\Na bell around Ikari’s neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A bell was there, but it didn’t ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A bell that doesn’t ring\Nserves no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll make sure the bell\Nworks next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:42.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My, my, what an unexpected situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:48.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How will you explain to\Nthe committee...  I mean, how will\Nyou explain this to SEELE?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:52.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01 wasn’t under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:58.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01 will remain frozen until the\Ncommittee gives us further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s a very appropriate decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:03.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, isn’t your son\Nstill trapped inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:09.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s hopeless.  It’s not accepting the\Ncode to eject the entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about the backup codes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:14.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Also refused.  Even a direct circuit\Nisn’t getting through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The plug’s video monitor\Nis active, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Switching to main screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What in the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d say that’s the truth behind\Na 400% synch ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:28.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe it.\NWhat happened to Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Apparently the Eva has taken\Nhim into itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What does that mean?!\NJust what is an Eva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:39.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It is something created by man in\Nman’s own image.  I really can’t\Ndescribe it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You didn’t create anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You just copied something you\Nfound in the Antarctic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What was the original?\NThat’s what I want to know, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is not just a copy.\NA human will is inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you saying somebody willed\Nthis to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, the Eva did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do something, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You created this, didn’t you?!\NTake responsibility for it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,On the issue of the Nansa Islands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the government and the Ministry of\NInternal Affairs have announced that\Nthere is no federal involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:14.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In other news, it has been a\Nmonth since the terrorist\Nincident in Tokyo-2...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and the government has announced\Nnew legislation to prevent another...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I’m still alive.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}...and the government has announced\Nnew legislation to prevent another...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know that Wonder Girl is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why are you bothering me with trivial\Ncrap like that, Misato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:33.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe it.\NI couldn’t do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe that stupid Shinji\Noutperformed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:43.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\Nyou’re going to “salvage” Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:47.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, theoretically, Shinji’s life\Nforce still exists in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And you’ll be respecting\Nthat life this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Losing Shinji is out of\Nthe question now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:57.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What NERV wants is Unit 01\Nas their tool, not Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:06.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Our assumption is that Shinji’s body\Nlost its Ego border and he’s floating in\Nthe entry plug in quantum form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:11.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re saying that Shinji has shifted\Ninto a form we can’t see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:19.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, the LCL has chemically altered\Ninto something very similar to the\Nsea water of primitive Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You mean, like a primordial soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:25.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All of the substances which composed\NShinji are still preserved in the plug...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:28.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and his soul exists there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:33.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In fact, his Ego image is giving a sort\Nof substance to his plug suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:38.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In other words, this salvage operation\Nmust both reconstruct his body\Nand fix his soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,With the MAGI’s support, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is all theoretical, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You won’t know what will really\Nhappen until you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In the entry plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:08:01.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s right.  But there’s nobody here.\NNot even myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?  What is this?\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,These people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:14.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, they’re people I know.\NPeople who know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I understand now.  This is my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:22.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be my world,\Nbut this I don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,An image from outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A hostile image?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s right!  The enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Enemy!  Enemy!  Enemy!  Enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Our enemies are something called\NAngels, they have the names\Nof the Angels, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They are the targets of\NEva and NERV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is our revenge for the\Ndeath of Misato’s father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:45.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why do I fight?\NDespite all the pain and suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:53.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,An unknown enemy is attacking us,\Nof course we have to fight them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Am I odd to try to find\Na reason to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Am I not supposed to think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Enemy!  Enemy!  Enemy!  Enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All are my enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:07.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Us...  That which threatens us\Nis the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:11.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course, how can I be faulted\Nfor protecting my own life and\Nthose of others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Enemy!  Enemy!  Enemy!  Enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My enemy!  My enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it!  Damn it!  Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You hurt Toji and killed my mother!\NFather!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why do you hate your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:42.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anyone would hate such a father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You don’t understand him, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NI’ve hardly ever seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:49.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that why you hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:54.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes!  My father doesn’t need me!\NMy father deserted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And am I his substitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes!!  It must be so!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He abandoned me because\Nhe had Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As if you didn’t run away\Nall by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:08.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shut up!  Shut up!  Shut up!\NIt’s all his fault!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That time I was actually going\Nto tell him I hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:19.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Did you tell me to pilot this just\Nto make me suffer, Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That can’t be true!  It can’t be!\NHow can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:26.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You don’t need me, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I called you because you had a use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because there was no one\Nelse who could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:41.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No way, I’ve never seen this before!\NIt’s impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, I knew it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s true!  I knew Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:52.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then I escaped!  I really escaped!\NLeaving my father and mother behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:05.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The concentration of LCL is\Ncurrently stable at 36%.  No problem\Nwith oxygen concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Electromagnetic radiation pulse is\Nnormal.  Wave pattern is 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Counters are functioning normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Salvage Plan Guideline\Nand Procedures...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:18.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s amazing that you could create\Nall this in only one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thanks for giving me credit,\Nbut it wasn’t my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This was already experimental\Nten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:26.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This kind of thing happened\Nduring the development?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:29.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was before I worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:33.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My mother was here, though.\NI only know the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And how did it come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve heard they failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this the warmth of a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was never aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:01.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was never aware of it,\Nbut now I think I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:07.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was never aware of it,\Nbut now I think I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:11.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are others kind to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because I am Eva’s pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because I pilot Eva,\Nthey treat me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:23.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That is the reason I can exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That is the everything to support\Nmy reason to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, I must pilot Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:34.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, I must fight what they\Nall call the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And I must win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Right, I can’t lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As they tell me to, I must pilot Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As they tell me to, I must win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Get to work, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good work, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:07.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato, Ritsuko, Asuka,\NToji, Kensuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They all respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,When I pilot Eva, they all respect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They respect this worthless being.\NEveryone says to pilot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:20.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll prove to my dad I’m worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, I’m doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Somebody be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:34.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I fought so hard.  I’m doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Treat me well!  Be nice to me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Tell me, Shinji, do you want\Nto become one with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,To be of one mind and body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It could be very, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ask me anytime.  I’m ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:03.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji-idiot, don’t you want\Nto be one with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,To be of one mind and body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It could be very, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:13.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You ought to appreciate your\Ngood fortune.  Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:17.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari, do you want to become\None with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,To be of one mind and body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It could be very, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do you want to become one with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,To be of one mind and body and soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It could be very, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Relax and release your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All investigative needles fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fixed at electromagnetic radius\Nof 0 minus 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ego border pulse\Nconnection is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Start salvage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.  Transmitting first signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:52.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva has received the signal.\NNo rejection confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Proceeding to second and third signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Subject cathexis is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Destrudo is not confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.  Shift the subject to stage two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji-idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yo, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:12.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji-idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:13.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:14.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yo, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:15.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:16.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji-idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:17.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:18.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:18.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yo, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:19.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:19.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji-idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:20.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yo, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:21.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:27.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s no good.  The Ego borderline\Nis frozen in a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Irradiate the wave patterns in\Nall directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:34.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It won’t work.  The signals are\Ntrapped in Klein space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:35.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It means we failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Abort intervention!  Reverse tangent\Nplug!  Return additions to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:46.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Destrudo reaction in the old area!\NPattern Sepia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:50.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A change is confirmed on the core\Npulse, too!  Plus 0.3 is confirmed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Maintenance of the status quo is top\Npriority!  Prevent backflow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Plus 0.5!  0.8!  This is odd!\NI can’t stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:02.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?!  Why?  Don’t you want\Nto come back, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:10.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I...  I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What do you wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What do you wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva has rejected the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:24.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,LCL self-replenishment is dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pressure in the plug is increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Abort all operations!  Cut the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:30.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It doesn’t work!  Plug is being ejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:45.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Inside of Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Inside of Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did I pilot Eva again?  Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You won’t pilot the Eva anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:56.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I decided I will never pilot Eva again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But you have just piloted\NEvangelion Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:04.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, you are here because you\Nhave piloted the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Piloting the Eva has created\Nyour present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:13.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You can never deny your past, Shinji,\Nnor can you deny the fact that you\Ndid indeed pilot it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That which is, is.  It’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you that\Nonly you can decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:26.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I....  I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:33.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What good is your damned science?!\NIt can’t even save one small life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:37.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Give me back my Shinji!\NGive him back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A human smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ayanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, not them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the smell of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:04.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Second Impact has occurred.\NWill he live in this hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:09.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anywhere can be heaven\Nif you try to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:14.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because he has a life, as long\Nas he lives, he will have the chance\Nto attain happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, you’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have you decided yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:26.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If it’s a boy, Shinji.\NIf it’s a girl, I’ll name the baby Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji...  Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
