Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:35.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see.\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:45.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Seeing her man as soon\Nas Shinji is saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I can’t criticize her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:55.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ritsuko must be thinking\NI’m pretty disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Appearing to give in to our sexual\Ndesires makes for a more realistic\Nand human appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We might even fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fool the intelligence department?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:05.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or the Commander and Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:08.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I meant myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You want to fool the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:18.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You never show interest in others,\Nbut you want their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You really are just like my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A cigarette?\NI didn’t know you still smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:27.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I only smoke after this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:30.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So nobody knows but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see, I’m honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:39.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And how’s Instrumentality going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:42.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Adam could wipe out mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why is it being kept there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did you come to see me\Njust to learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:52.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, that’s one of the reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:58.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It would be my honor to be used as\Nmy lady’s cat’s-paw, but I can’t\Ntell you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just want you to know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:06.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are NERV and Commander Ikari\Nreally planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d like to know that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:18.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, you can’t dodge my\Nquestions by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t put strange things in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe this.  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:56.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here’s a present for you,\Nthe first time in eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And maybe the last as well.
